Invocation Name: new tree
des:
Imagine, every meal you eat, you have no idea what going into your food.

New Tree can help you eat healthy. Say: Alexa! ask New Tree to give me a Burrito or Say: Alexa! ask New Tree give me a Pizza

For health facts, you can also ask New Tree to pick a Fact Fruit. Start a new healthy life, planting a New Tree now


(Will have regular updates to keep you engaged.)
-Skill by Johnny
